Author: vchat-meme-blip <limeikenji@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Mar 29 05:17:06 2026 +0200

    feat(local-llm): 8.8 tool-use / function calling via fllama
    
    Add multi-turn local tool dispatch loop to LocalLlmService.chat():
    - _localTools: get_current_datetime (extensible)
    - _dispatchLocalTool(): synchronous tool dispatcher
    - _runChatTurn(): streams text deltas, accumulates tool_calls across
      streaming chunks (fllama delta pattern), dispatches local tools on
      finish_reason=tool_calls, then recurses with updated message list
      (depth limit 3, OpenAI wire format tool_calls messages)
    - chat() delegates to _runChatTurn(); stop() closes _activeChatController
    - Remove stale gateway_state.dart import
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

