commit 17fcb452002711a759d3d1e2283e4d29ab9d34fc
Author: vchat-meme-blip <limeikenji@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Mar 28 22:28:59 2026 +0200

    feat(local-llm): replace gateway provider path with direct :8081 inference
    
    - All local-llm inference (text, vision, video) now bypasses OpenClaw
      gateway entirely and POSTs directly to llama-server on port 8081
    - Replace broken llama.cpp ZIP download (no Ubuntu ARM64 binary exists
      in official releases) with npm-based node-llama-cpp standalone server:
      writes server.js + package.json to /root/.openclaw/, PRoot runs
      mkdir + npm install to get @node-llama-cpp/linux-arm64 prebuilt addon
    - Fix mkdir race: Flutter-side Directory.create() not visible in PRoot
      namespace; now PRoot does its own mkdir -p before cd/npm install
    - Remove dead "Route to local model" toggle (now no-op, wrong subtitle)
    - Add Health Check button + server log viewer to Diagnostics Playground
    - sendMessageHttp gains directUrl param for llama-server bypass
    - sendVisionMessage + analyseVideoFrames point to :8081 directly
    - Drop --log-disable from tmux launch; stdout captured to llama-server.log
    - startWithModel no-op guard: skip restart if model already running
    - Remove dead _isNodeLlamaCppReady, _llamaBuild, getLlamaServerZipUrl
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

