      24s vs 90s — eliminates the cascading 7-10 min startup stall.
    
    - Re-add battery optimization check to spawn path (was removed): Android
      battery optimization silently kills PRoot, causing restart loops that
      extend startup time. Now warns in logs and requests exemption.
    
