      + verify local-llm provider is enabled in config — fast, no port 8081
    - Remove dead _llamaHost/_llamaPort fields (8081 no longer used)
    - Video analysis analyseVideoFrames(): update base URL from hardcoded
      127.0.0.1:8081 to AppConstants.gatewayUrl so vision requests reach
      the gateway's OpenAI-compat endpoint
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

